sshfp (1.2.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release:
    - Fix -4 / -6 flags
    - Throw errors on stderr to improve pipe usage
    - openSUSE package information on import error
    - Fix nameserver by IP address (ldns workaround)
    - Fix case where AAAA is found but no IPv6 is available
  * Fix watch file
  * Remove useless empty dh_auto_build override 
  * Remove X-Python-Version field as I am unsure which is the minimum
    supported python version 

